| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5895 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 51ebaa72-4657-5fc5-83d4-7cf037510f62"
